{"prompt": "Generate a website for a video game studio. The website should be bold and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Quantum Leap Studios</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            background-color: #0a0a2a; /* Dark blue background */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            scroll-behavior: smooth;\n        }\n        .hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(rgba(10, 10, 42, 0.9), rgba(10, 10, 42, 0.7)), url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1506748686214-e9df14d4d9d0?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1170&q=80'); /* Dark blue gradient with an image */\n            background-size: cover;\n            background-position: center;\n            height: 100vh;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            text-align: center;\n            flex-direction: column;\n        }\n        .hero h1 {\n            font-size: 5em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 255, 0.5);\n        }\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            color: #cccccc;\n        }\n        nav {\n            background-color: #000033; /* Deep blue */\n            padding: 15px 0;\n            position: sticky;\n            top: 0;\n            z-index: 1000;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n        }\n        nav ul {\n            list-style: none;\n            padding: 0;\n            margin: 0;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n        }\n        nav ul li {\n            margin: 0 20px;\n        }\n        nav ul li a {\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        nav ul li a:hover {\n            color: #4682b4; /* Steel blue for hover */\n        }\n        .section {\n            padding: 80px 40px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        .section h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            color: #4682b4; /* Steel blue for section titles */\n        }\n        .game-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n        .game-card {\n            background-color: #000033; /* Deep blue */\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .game-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 255, 0.4);\n        }\n        .game-card img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 200px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n        }\n        .game-card-content {\n            padding: 20px;\n        }\n        .game-card-content h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n        }\n        .game-card-content p {\n            color: #cccccc;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: #4682b4; /* Steel blue */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #6495ed; /* Cornflower blue */\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: #000033; /* Deep blue */\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 40px 0;\n            margin-top: 60px;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            color: #cccccc;\n        }\n        footer a {\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header class=\"hero\">\n        <h1>Quantum Leap Studios</h1>\n        <p>Crafting Immersive Worlds, One Pixel at a Time.</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <ul>\n            <li><a href=\"#about\">About Us</a></li>\n            <li><a href=\"#games\">Our Games</a></li>\n            <li><a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a></li>\n        </ul>\n    </nav>\n\n    <section id=\"about\" class=\"section\">\n        <h2>About Us</h2>\n        <p>We are a passionate team of developers, artists, and storytellers dedicated to creating unforgettable gaming experiences. Our focus is on innovation, cutting-edge technology, and compelling narratives that push the boundaries of interactive entertainment.</p>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"games\" class=\"section\">\n        <h2>Our Games</h2>\n        <div class=\"game-grid\">\n            <div class=\"game-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517336714731-489689fd1ca8?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1170&q=80\" alt=\"Game 1\">\n                <div class=\"game-card-content\">\n                    <h3>Chronos Rift</h3>\n                    <p>Embark on an epic journey through time, facing futuristic enemies and ancient mysteries. A sci-fi RPG with a branching narrative.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"game-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503454505-34c71299848b?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1170&q=80\" alt=\"Game 2\">\n                <div class=\"game-card-content\">\n                    <h3>Whispering Woods</h3>\n                    <p>Explore a magical forest filled with secrets and challenges. A captivating puzzle-adventure game.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"game-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1557888784-7c11a460c6a5?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1170&q=80\" alt=\"Game 3\">\n                <div class=\"game-card-content\">\n                    <h3>Cybernetic Dawn</h3>\n                    <p>Navigate the neon-drenched streets of a dystopian future. A fast-paced action-shooter with cybernetic enhancements.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\">View All Games</a>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\" class=\"section\">\n        <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n        <p>Have a business inquiry, a question, or just want to say hello? We'd love to hear from you!</p>\n        <a href=\"mailto:info@quantumleapstudios.com\" class=\"cta-button\">Contact Us</a>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Quantum Leap Studios. All rights reserved.</p>\n        <p>Follow us on <a href=\"#\">Social Media</a></p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}